    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved specimen, offered in showroom-ready condition. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, having been maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. For the discerning buyer seeking an unrivaled acquisition without compromise, this vehicle stands as a definitive benchmark in quality and performance.",
