    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L atmospheric inline-six features individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering razor-sharp throttle response up to its 8,000 RPM redline. This unit is mechanically impeccable, having undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using cryo-treated components. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power through a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight and quiet. The chassis exhibits zero compliance issues, with the suspension geometry and bushings maintained to factory specifications. Finished in its original paint with no evidence of oxidation or clear-coat failure, this is a turn-key, collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
